               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="259v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1560Gospel">Four Gospels</title>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="3r" to="39v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1558Matthew">Gospel of Matthew</title>
                        <note>
                           The title is: <q xml:lang="gez">ብስራተ፡ ማቴዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ፩እም፲ወ፪ሐዋርያት፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ፍቁሩ።</q>. 
                           The text is followed by a note of composition of the gospel on <locus target="#39v"/>: 
                           <q xml:lang="gez">መልአ፡ ብስራተ፡ 
                                 <sic>መቴዎስ፡</sic>
                               ሐዋርያ፨ ወኮነ፡ ጸሐፎ፡ በምድረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡ በአስተሐምሞ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፨ 
                              እብራይስጣዌ፨ 
                                 <sic>ዘበአጶርግዮ፡</sic>
                               ለኀበ፡ ሰማይ፡ በ፰ዓመት፡ ወበቀዳሚት፡ ዓም፡ 
                                 <sic>ዘእቀላውዴዎን፡</sic>
                               ቄሣር፡ 
                              ንጉሠ፡ ሮም፨ ወስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓ፨ ለ፨ ም፨ አ፨ ሜ፨ ን፨</q>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="40r" to="59v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1882MarkGo">Gospel of Mark</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                           <locus from="40"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1882MarkGo#TituliMark">Wangel za-Mārqos, Tituli of the Gospel of Mark</title>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
                           <locus from="41r" to="59v"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2711Mark">Bǝsrāta Mārqos</title>
                           <note>
                              The text is followed by a note of composition of the gospel on <locus target="#59v"/>:
                              <q xml:lang="gez">
                                 ተፈጸመ፡ ብሥራተ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ሐዋርያ፤ እንተ፡ ጸሐፎ፡ በልሳነ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ዕርገቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ በሥጋ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማይ፨ በ፲ወ፩ዓመት፨ ወበራብዕት፡ ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለቀላውዴዎስ፡ 
                                 ቄሣር፨ ሎቱ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                              </q>.
                           </note>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="60r" to="95"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1812GospelLuke">Gospel of Luke</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.1">
                           <locus from="60r" to="95"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2713Luke">Bǝsrāta Luqās</title>
                           <note>
                              The text is followed by a note of composition of the gospel on <locus target="#95"/>:
                              <q xml:lang="gez">
                                 መልዓ፡ ብስራተ፡ <choice>
                                    <sic>ሉቃሉ፡</sic>
                                    <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ሉቃስ፡</corr>
                                 </choice> ሐዋርያ፡ ጠቢብ፡ እንተ፡ 
                                 <choice>
                                    <sic>ተሐፋ፡</sic>
                                    <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ጸሐፋ፡</corr>
                                 </choice> በልሳነ፡ ጽርዕ፡ ለሰብአ፡ ሀገረ፡ መቄዶንያ፡ እምድኅረ፡ 
                                 ዕርገቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማይ፡ በ፳ወ፪ዓመት፨ ወበ፲ወ፬ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለቀላውዴዎስ፡ ቄሳር፨ ወስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                              </q>.
                           </note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.2">
                           <locus target="#95"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1812GospelLuke#TituliLuke">Wangel za-Luqās, Tituli of the Gospel of Luke</title>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="96r" to="124v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                        <note>
                           The name of the owner, Walda Tǝnśāʾe (perhaps the same as <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName>), is mentioned in the 
                           supplication formula in the title: 
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ብስራተ፡ አብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ትሩፍ፡ ረድዕ፡ ተናጋሪ፡ በመለኮት፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ዘብዴዎስ፡ ፍቁረ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ ወኃብተ፡ ረድኤቱ፡ የሃሉ፡ ምስለ፡ 
                              ፍቁሩ፨ ወልደ፡ ትንሣኤ፨</q>. 
                           The text is followed by a note of composition of the gospel on <locus target="#39v"/>:
                           <q xml:lang="gez">መልአ፡ ብስራተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ዘብዴዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ፩እም፲ወ፪ሐዋርያት፡ ዘጸሐፎ፡ በዮናኒ፨ ለሰብአ፡ ኤፌሶን፨ እምድኅረ፡ እርገቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ በ፴ዓመት፡ ወበ፰ዓመተ፡ 
                              መንግሥቱ፡ ለኔሮን፡ ወልደ፡ አቅሎድዮስ፨ ወስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓለ<del rend="expunctuated">ዓ</del>መ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨</q>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus from="125r" to="128v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1560Gospel#IntroductionGospels">Introduction to the Gospels</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ንቀድም። በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር። ዘሎቱ፡ ስብሐት፡ ይትባረክ፡ 
                           ስሙ፡ ወይትለዓል፡ ዝክሩ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> በጽሒፈ፡ መቅድመ፡ ፬ወንጌላት፡ ቅዱሳት፡ 
                           ወ፲አቅማራት፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አሜን፨ ወእምድኅረ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ይሤኒ፡ ዘይቅድም፡ መቅድመ፡ ነገር፡ ፍሡሕ።
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           ወለኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ አእመኑ፡ በዛህን፡ ዘእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ መርሰ፡ አብዑ፡ መጥዎ፡ በእንተ፡ ኅብረተ፡ ቃላት፡ ዘቅዱሳን፡ ፬ወንጌላት፡ ተፈጸመ።
                        </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                        <locus target="#128v"/>
                        <title>On the composition of the gospel of Matthew</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           በስመ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ መዓርገ፡ ወንጌላት፡ ወዝማሬ፡ ዘበአማን፡ በተአምራት፡ ግሁዳት፨ እምኀበ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ 
                           ወመንክ<del rend="expunctuated">ር</del>ራት፡ መዋዔ፡ ኵሉ፡ ልቡናት፨
                        </incipit>
                        <note>
                           The praise continuates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">
                              
                                 <sic>ወለመቴዎስሰ፡</sic>
                               ስሙ፡ ሌዊ፡ ወትርጓሜሁ፡ ኅሩይ፨ ወውእቱ፡ እምነገደ፡ 
                              ይሳኮር፡ እምሀገረ፡ ናዝሬት፨ በስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ዲቁ፡ ወስመ፡ እሙ፡ ኪሩትያስ፡</q>.
                        </note>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           ወተቀብረ፡ በቅርጣግና፡ ዘቂሣርያ። ወለዛቲሰ፡ ብስራት፡ ተርጐማ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ዘብዴዎስ፡ እልአልሳን፡ ወሰበከ፡ ባቲ፡ በህንድ፤ ወኢየሩሳሌም፡ ወስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ 
                        </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                        <locus from="129r" to="131v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1560Gospel#IntroductionCanons">Four Gospels, Canons of Eusebius (same as LIT1224Canons)</title>
                        <note/>
